&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for a driven and commercially sharp Senior Partner Development Executive to spearhead our launch into Greece. This is a rare opportunity to be the first on the ground — building our partner and channel ecosystem from scratch and establishing our presence in a high-potential territory. You&#39;ll work closely with the global sales and partnerships teams to define the go-to-market strategy, identify and onboard the right channel partners, and drive revenue through indirect sales motion&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
