&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Company Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Redpin we&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;simplify life&#39;s most important payments.&lt;/strong&gt; Buying a new property overseas can be a stressful time, especially when it comes to moving your money. Through our Currencies Direct and TorFX brands we&#39;ve been helping people do just that for over 25 years. With recent investment we&#39;re now on a mission to build a new range of digital products and services that will make moving money Internationally for Real Estate purchases even easier. &lt;strong&gt;We’re on a mission to become the solution for Real Estate &amp;amp; B2B payments everywhere&lt;/strong&gt; . To do this, we are transitioning our business from a horizontal FX platform to a verticalized, embedded software company, as we look to the future and Redpin 2.0&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;In this role, you will be the strategic architect behind how &lt;strong&gt;Redpin&lt;/strong&gt; (powered by Currencies Direct) wins the Spanish market. As a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Product Marketing Manager&lt;/strong&gt;, you are responsible for more than just &quot;marketing&quot;—you are the bridge between our customers’ pain points and our technical solutions. You will spend your time dissecting the complex processes of notaries, conveyancers, and real estate agents to ensure our real-time payment platform is perfectly fit for purpose.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Market &amp;amp; Persona Intelligence (50%):&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with the Product Director to analyze the banking sector, local regulations, and customer workflows. You’ll meet with partners to &quot;test the water&quot; with mock-ups and identify gaps where our technology can provide the most value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales Enablement &amp;amp; Content (25%):&lt;/strong&gt; Equipping our BDEs and Product Specialists on the ground. You will create the internal content, pitch decks, and objection-handling guides needed to win the &quot;sign-off&quot; from skeptical buyers and sellers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Local Market Activation (25%):&lt;/strong&gt; Plan and oversee local marketing events and affiliate initiatives across Spain to drive brand awareness and lead generation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Feedback Loop:&lt;/strong&gt; Collect regional feedback to influence the global roadmap, ensuring that features like &quot;Deposit Management&quot; solve the specific cash-flow and security concerns of international buyers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security Evangelism:&lt;/strong&gt; Position our platform as the &quot;Safe Haven&quot; against cyber-attacks and IBAN spoofing, turning security into a core competitive advantage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Need&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Seniority &amp;amp; Experience:&lt;/strong&gt; At least &lt;strong&gt;8 years&lt;/strong&gt; of experience in Product Marketing. We are looking for a &quot;perfect fit&quot; profile that blends Product Marketing Management with a background in general Marketing/Events.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;High Analytical IQ:&lt;/strong&gt; You need the ability to digest the &quot;rocket science&quot; of the banking sector and simplify it into clear, value-driven solutions for the product team and customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Spanish Market Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt; A deep understanding of how business is done in Spain, particularly the relationship between buyers, sellers, and notaries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;At Redpin we simplify life&#39;s most important payments. Buying a new property overseas can be a stressful time, especially when it comes to moving your money. Through our Currencies Direct and TorFX brands we&#39;ve been helping people do just that for over 25 years. With recent investment we&#39;re now on a mission to build a new range of digital products and services that will make moving money Internationally for Real Estate purchases even easier&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Redpin is now looking for several Product Sales Specialists in Spain. These are new positions focused on developing sales of one of our new flagship payment products, set to revolutionise the Property buying process. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;About the role&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We have recently launched a new payments solution that will revolutionise paying for property in Spain- Redpin Payments. This software is designed with Conveyancers in mind&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;As a Product Sales Specialist, you will be part of a new sales team that will help revolutionise how conveyancers process payments for Real Estate. Using a consultative approach, you will prospect, build relationships and sign up new conveyancing customers in your area. By understanding their needs, you will develop a customized solution to help them thrive. You will also help to build and establish our brand in this new segment for your geographical territory.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This is a field-based role.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;What you’ll do&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Generate list of prospective conveyancing firms and manage the entire sales cycle from initial chat to close&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;You will run multiple open opportunities at any given time (both new and upsell).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&g

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;At Redpin, &lt;/strong&gt;our mission is to bring global citizens and businesses together by simplifying life’s most important payments. Our world-class payments network and human-centric customer service touches a vast global community across 15,000+ partners, 235 territories and two flagship brands,&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;Currencies Direct and TorFX. We are reshaping the age-old property market by connecting the dots across the entire ecosystem, from buyers and sellers to legal service firms and title companies to property management, banks and real estate agents.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the UAE specifically, our vision is to become the trusted international payments infrastructure for all property transactions, starting with developers. We are regulated by the DFSA with an office in the DIFC; This role is the commercial engine of our MENA expansion — the licence is in place, the first developer partnerships are signed, and the market is ready to be built.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a senior individual contributor sales role. You will own Redpin&#39;s revenue and pipeline in the UAE — identifying, pursuing, and closing the developer partnerships that make Redpin the default cross-border payments infrastructure in the market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The foundation is in place: DFSA regulation, DIFC presence, and initial developer partnerships. What we need now is a commercially excellent salesperson who can build aggressively on that base — someone who understands the developer ecosystem deeply, can operate at C-suite level, and can translate Redpin&#39;s technical capabilities into compelling commercial value for developer audiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is not a management role. There is no team to run. Your output is revenue. Your success will dictate the future planned hiring of addition salespeople in the region so a future leadership&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Will Own&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Revenue &amp;amp; Pipeline&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Own and deliver Redpin&#39;s commercial targets in the UAE&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Build and manage a structured pipeline of real estate developer partnerships — off-plan, master developer, and mid-tier&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Drive full-cycle deal execution: origination, qualification, commercial negotiation, and close&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Develop direct origination channels with developer sales teams, project finance functions, and overseas investment desks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Developer Partnerships&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
