&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build &amp;amp; Enhance APIs:&lt;/strong&gt; Design, develop, and maintain high-quality APIs powering web and mobile experiences.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive Performance &amp;amp; Security:&lt;/strong&gt; Ensure systems meet high standards for performance, reliability, and security across all layers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
